column5: They are calling for        ,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Wait for it     ,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Wait,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,     +11 for Tuesday here
Let's hope it's not too long.
Lets hope it is.LOL I like the nature walks.
x2  I want to get some more ice fishing in
Thats good ice out there with a good snow blanket, i think it will stay put to some degree, but certainly wont be the same great ice.
You forgot to mention the rain.
Warming all the way up to -24 here tomorrow!!! Then back down to -30 on Tuesday.
It would be nice to give the ice guys a good couple mths though!!!.
+3C over here Wednesday... time for a day off to chase some pokadots   Then it's back down below zero
It will be good Brian.. especially with rain.. it will get rid of the snow cover and leave the ice ready for the next deep freeze, to make real ice.

I used to like u misfish lol,    as we were from Barrie and all .  Winter is  awesome at least up here. Still -40 windchills at night. Went up to a balmy -24 today, enough to melt off the frost from the windows, can see outside again  . Colder air coming here again next week thankfully, We'll try to send some more down you way for those hard water fishermen and women. Nature walks are those romantic gushy things you do in the summer  .lol
All you'll be seeing is dbl/dbl if you plan on breaking out the float gear, lol.
Pfffftt... Practically tropical compared to where I've been hanging out lately
